      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "HvNVtc06q8Tf"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "This project aims to evaluate whether simple trading strategies can generate profit using historical stock data.\n",
        "\n",
        "We analyze different strategies such as daily trading and RSI-based trading, and evaluate their performance using metrics like win rate, average return, and final capital.\n",
        "\n",
        "The goal is to understand whether these strategies provide a real edge in the market."
      ],
